OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and sunny start to the
OL,6,Fmorning. A very warm afternoon to
OL,7,Fcome, though the sunshine turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy later on. An
OL,9,Fisolated heavy shower may also be
OL,10,Fpossible. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mostly dry evening and
OL,13,Fnight with plenty of clear spells.
OL,14,FSome low cloud developing over the
OL,15,Fhills during the early hours. Staying
OL,16,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
