OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome low cloud first thing,
OL,6,Fwith perhaps an isolated light shower.
OL,7,FSkies brightening by lunchtime, with
OL,8,Fplenty of sunshine developing.
OL,9,FGenerally feeling fresher than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fbright start to Saturday, but heavy
OL,13,Frain moving in later on in the day.
OL,14,FSunshine and showers for Sunday and
OL,15,Fthen potentially wetter and winder on
OL,16,FMonday. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
